---
title: Turkey & Black Bean Queso Bowls with Tomato Salsa, Lime & Cilantro
description: Creamy queso blanco levels up these hearty rice bowls topped with spiced ground turkey, black beans, and a zesty homemade tomato-cilantro salsa. A final squeeze of fresh lime juice makes the perfect tangy finishing touch. Best of all, it's all on the table in a speedy 20 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67e11a827594446a7cdcbac0-ea9d019b.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67e11a827594446a7cdcbac0-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/turkey-and-black-bean-queso-bowls-67e11a827594446a7cdcbac0
servings: 2
cuisine: Central America
nutrition:
  calories: 940 kcal
  fat: 31 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 106 g
  sugar: 8 g
  protein: 46 g
  fiber: 9 g
